0. 0rth Law (as in thermodynamics)
cat LICENSE

1. compile 
$ make

2. INsert the module into kernel and setup the system
$ keyboard_stats_load

3. Read the statistics
$ cat /dev/keyboard_stats | less

4. Remove the module
$ keyboard_stats_unload


DEBUGGING
---------

Mail the author or read /var/log/messages and set the scancodes.



